name: - Majestic mountain (Nepal series #8) -
description:
When you are still at the very bottom of your journey, you look at these mountains and think it's unattainable to reach the top. But step by step, we get to our destination. Remember to enjoy the journey and not worry too much about the outcome. If you are driven by passion and love, the rest will take care of itself.
